             the constable, and Samuel</p>
               <p>'Sawyer, a servant to Mr. Rowlet, confirmed</p>
               <p>'Mr. Rowlet's testimony.'</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I was going to sell it for my master.</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. I don't sell any retail; I never gave him authority to sell for me.</p>
